commitResults.messageTitle: Implemented skeletal version of Duke with echo and exit functionality.
commitResults.messageBody: Added a Response class to deal with string formatting for responses.

commitResults.messageTitle: Implemented adding of items to list. Implemented listing of stored items.

1) Implemented marking of tasks as completed. 2) Added a Task class to represent an individual Task. 3) Added a Tasklist class to handle the storing of Tasks in a list. 4) Edited Response.java to handle the printing of formatted strings as well.
Added tracking for ToDo, Event and Deadline tasks. 1) Implemented counting of total tasks in list on addition of task. 2) Added individual classes for each task type to handle individual behaviour.

Performed semi-automated testing of text UI 1) Tested basic functionality (startup text, event, todo, deadline, list, done, bye) 2) Fixed a bug where created events' descriptions would appear twice in the UI, stray print statement in code.

Added error handling for multiple edge cases. 1) Handled cases where the input to "done" is not a number or out of range. 2) Handled cases where "todo" is called without a valid description. 3) Handled cases where "deadline" is called without a valid description or due date. 4) Handled cases where "event" is called without a valid description or event date.
Implemented delete functionality for tasks. 1) Fixed error handling for "done" when no argument was given.
Implemented bug fix for parsing 1) Split by " /at " and " /by " for events and deadlines respectively instead of "/at" and "/by".
